did.unittitle: Cornell University Women's Studies Program records, 1968-1997.
did.repository: Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library
did.abstract: Records of department faculty and speakers; course lists; seminars; annual reports and other material.

bioghist.head: ORGANIZATIONAL HISTORY
bioghist.p: Women's Studies was renamed Feminist, Gender & Sexuality Studies (FGSS) in 2002.
